column1: #text=On Saturday , I woke up to a nice day and realized that I had some free times on my hands .
#text=I decided to do a little baking to enjoy my day and relax .
#text=I have always enjoyed baking and this would be the perfect opportunity to bake something for my grandmother , who 's birthday was right around the corner .
#text=I got out the cake mix , the frosting and the sprinkles and started baking the cake .
#text=I put all of the cake mix into a big bowl and began to stir it .
#text=I then put the cake mix into a pan for cooking and pre-heated my oven .
#text=After my oven was done pre-heating I placed the pan into the oven .
#text=I waited for it to finish before taking out the freshly baked cake .
#text=I then took the frosting and brushed it against the outside of the cake .
#text=Following that I tossed some sprinkles on the top to make it look nice .
#text=I then put it in the fridge to save for my grandmother .
